author: julianfoad
msg: In the merge code, remove an unused counter and other non-functional tweaks.
do_merge): Stop counting notifications, since the result wasn't used and
we weren't counting them accurately anyway.
(single_file_merge_notify): Declare the data type of the notify baton,
because we know what it must be.
(do_merge): Remove a redundant initialization: we don't know whether it's
a single-file merge at this point, but we already set it later on where
